<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是<delay8 />昆蟲與我的……<delay20 />
一對一對決！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了這一天，<delay8 />
我練習了捕蟲，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果到現在，我還是連一隻都抓不到<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要說捕蟲的訣竅，<delay20 />
果然還是要去配合牠的呼吸嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在真的將魚釣上來以前，<delay20 />
都不知道會釣到什麼魚，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這也算是釣魚的有趣之處吧。<pageBreak />這種讓人期待的感覺，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就好像節慶活動時的<delay8 />
抽獎遊戲一樣呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要細心地好好照顧，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />花朵們也會像是回應這份心意<delay8 />
一樣努力綻放呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然花朵不會說話，<delay20 />
所以沒辦法用言語跟它們溝通，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我總覺得能夠跟它們心靈相通呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果能用我最喜歡的雨傘，<delay20 />
和我最喜歡的人<delay8 />
一起撐傘的話<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇啊～<delay20 />光是想像一下，<delay8 />
就覺得很害羞呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>